properties.Name: InsuranceStatementLineItem
properties.Description: A reportable line item detail of the associated Insurance Statement.

Columns.Name: InsurancePolicyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Insurance Policy.

Columns.Name: StatementDate
Columns.Description: The date of the Insurance Statement.

Columns.Name: StatementLineItemNumber
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Statement Line Item.

Columns.Name: TransactionId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Transaction.

Columns.Name: Amount
Columns.Description: The amount of the transaction or current amount reported.

Columns.Name: StatementLineItemTypeId
Columns.Description:
The unique identifier of an Insurance Statement Line Type.

Ex:

- Premium paid
- Current death benefit
- Interest credited
- Loans outstanding
- Monthly charges
- Cash surrender value

Columns.Name: InsuranceStatementLineItemNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the associated line item.
